      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "UR-MU @ Bukit Bintang is a one-of-a-kind quirky art museum located in the center of Kuala Lumpur.The collection is eclectic, regional and conveys some of the aspirations and moods of the recent era.Featuring artworks across 10 themed gallery spaces, a roof-top sculpture garden and a Balinese garden to commemorate the late landscape maestro from Bali Pak Made Wijaya.UR-MU, like all forms of art, is for all to enjoy."
          }
        ]
      },
